"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![](https://miro.medium.com/max/1400/1\\\\*19ac7mjFDvIP5ukECuYT3w.png)\\n\\n## “WePiggy’s Billionaires” on Harmony\\n\\nIn order to encourage users to participate in WePiggy-Harmony lending protocol, the WePiggy-Harmony “WePiggy’s Billionaires” activity is now open!\\n\\n**Activity time:**2021/12/30 15:00 (UTC+8) to WePiggy’s official launch on the next public chain or layer 2 network\\n\\n**Activity Rules:**\\n\\nDuring the activity, participate in WePiggy-Harmony WPC mining campaign, and the cumulative amount of mined WPC tokens ranks in the top **198** of the “WePiggy’s Billionaires”, will win the \\\\[ Harmony Exclusive Edition\\\\] \\\\[Epic Level\\\\] NFT — “**HarmonyPiggy**”.\\n\\n**Currently, WPC claim and cross-chain bridge functions are not available for the time being, and are expected to be enabled within one week.**\\n\\n**Please note:**\\n\\n1\\\\. The “**HarmonyPiggy**” NFT will be open for claim after the activity ends. Except for participating in this activity, or through the transfer of old holders in the future, no more “**HarmonyPiggy**” will be generated.\\n\\n2\\\\. WePiggy reserves the right of final interpretation of this activity.\\n\\n## Activity Participation Tutorial\\n\\n## About “HarmonyPiggy” NFT\\n\\nThis card is issued to commemorate the 8 step of WePiggy’s cross-chain deployment plan: Harmony.\\n\\nIn Harmony’s high-performance network, explore ways to make big money in DeFi. Holder of this NFT will be blessed by WePiggy with the buff of “Harmony Brings Wealth”.\\n\\n## Join the community\\n\\nWebsite: [https://wepiggy.com](https://wepiggy.com/)\\n\\nTwitter: <https://twitter.com/wepiggydotcom>\\n\\nMedium: [https://wepiggy-com.medium.com](https://wepiggy-com.medium.com/)\\n\\nTelegram: <https://t.me/wepiggy>\\n\\nForum: [https://gov.wepiggy.com](https://gov.wepiggy.com/)\\n\\nDiscord: <https://discord.gg/wepiggy>\\n\\nGithub: <https://github.com/WePiggy>\",\"timestamp\":1641545210,\"title\":\"“WePiggy’s Billionaires” WPC Mining Competition on Harmony Begins！\"},\"digest\":\"ckFShEYYppvSAgxFnzFDMP-hsggaQ3Mj5mfF_NbGAxA\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xf14a9FA917a5517867e4e0018f320c1F6BF6f182\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N058fbF2oH-5FRUnNLTMyeE3rf-G_BHzR0C8oeW7Iq0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qplgfXXk1tm_RlmpNgaRICzwQ_jygCJmICubkF3Ct8k\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"HLg7K18oa_OK-8iQzXIWQu3x1fFZ87f6uQpqrFuBfN4S3HsThOu89MRzY8d2VM-NU60Q-Tv2ipdulMcWIbKOxg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xb09510e4564695a83514694625f4542ed3f53eda5ab968255fe4def27a1d1be57643a01bb6126cf2d95f59f63f7362fabd4919eb5de0046cdad4810ae1f86fef1c\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"N058fbF2oH-5FRUnNLTMyeE3rf-G_BHzR0C8oeW7Iq0\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"qplgfXXk1tm_RlmpNgaRICzwQ_jygCJmICubkF3Ct8k\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"ckFShEYYppvSAgxFnzFDMP-hsggaQ3Mj5mfF_NbGAxA\"}"